2014年10月前，太空船2号已经进行了54次试飞。<ref name="space20141008">{{cite news |url=http://www.space.com/27376-virgin-galactic-spaceshiptwo-test-flight.html |title=Virgin Galactic's SpaceShipTwo Aces Glide Test Flight |work=Space.com |date=8 October 2014 |accessdate=8 October 2014 |last=Wall |first=Mike |archive-date=2014-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141104161902/http://www.space.com/27376-virgin-galactic-spaceshiptwo-test-flight.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>在这些飞行试验中飞船10次使用了它的“羽毛”翼布局。<ref name="space20141008" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.virgingalactic.com/news/item/feather-flight-and-nitrous-vent-test-success/|title=Feather flight and nitrous vent test success|publisher=Virgin Galactic|accessdate=12 April 2013|archive-date=2019-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191111051050/https://www.virgingalactic.com/news/item/feather-flight-and-nitrous-vent-test-success/|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name=pressrelease20140110>{{cite web |url=http://www.virgingalactic.com/news/item/virgin-galactic-reaches-new-heights-in-third-supersonic-test-flight/ |date=10 Jan 2014 |accessdate=13 Jan 2014 |title=Virgin Galactic Reaches New Heights in Third Supersonic Test Flight |work=virgingalactic.com |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407135714/http://www.virgingalactic.com/news/item/virgin-galactic-reaches-new-heights-in-third-supersonic-test-flight |archivedate=2014-04-07 }}</ref>

===2014年10月的意外===
[[File:NTSB_Go-Team_inspects_a_tail_section_of_VSS_Enterprise.jpg|thumb]]Go-Team在检查{{le|VSS企业号|VSS Enterprise}}的尾部部分。]]
2014年10月31日上午10時左右太空船2號就在脫離母船，準備繼續升空沒多久發生爆炸，隨即整架太空船斷成兩半快速墜落，墜毀在加州[[莫哈韦沙漠|莫哈韦沙漠]]當中。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bakersfieldcalifornian.com/local/x1143260271/SpaceShipTwo-experiences-in-flight-anomaly |title=SpaceShipTwo disaster: Industry mourns pilot but vows to keep ... - BakersfieldCalifornian.com |work=The Bakersfield Californian |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151023044651/http://www.bakersfieldcalifornian.com/local/x1143260271/SpaceShipTwo-experiences-in-flight-anomaly |archivedate=2015-10-23 |access-date=2014-11-03 }}</ref>从而导致一名飞行员受伤和另一名飞行员遇难死亡，是自2003年哥倫比亞號以來最嚴重的太空梭意外，也是第一次有人生還的[[太空飛機|太空飛機]]事故。<ref>{{cite web|title=Virgin Galactic’s SpaceShipTwo rocket plane crashes|date=October 31, 2014|url=http://spaceflightnow.com/2014/10/31/virgin-galactics-spaceshiptwo-suffers-anomaly-during-test-flight/|accessdate=2014-11-03|archive-date=2014-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141102185808/http://spaceflightnow.com/2014/10/31/virgin-galactics-spaceshiptwo-suffers-anomaly-during-test-flight/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[美国国家运输安全委员会|美国国家运输安全委员会]]的事故调查报告认为，副驾驶过快打开[[制动系统|制动系统]]的锁紧装置，导致飞船尾翼呈現下降衝形態，发生结构性破坏，使飞船在空气动力过载的情况下解体<ref>{{cite web|title=In-Flight Breakup During Test Flight Scaled Composites SpaceShipTwo, N339SS|url=http://www.ntsb.gov/news/events/Documents/2015_spaceship2_BMG_abstract.pdf|website=NTSB|accessdate=2015-12-23|date=October 31, 2014|archive-date=2015-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151223190522/http://www.ntsb.gov/news/events/Documents/2015_spaceship2_BMG_abstract.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

